  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de libcdio</title>

    <para>Install <application>libcdio</application> by running the
    following </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr --disable-static &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Pour tester le résultat, tapez : <command>make check</command>.</para>

    <para>Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>
    user:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

    <para>Now install libcdio-paranoia:</para>

<screen><userinput>tar -xf ../libcdio-paranoia-10.2+&libcdio-version;+1.tar.bz2 &amp;&amp;
cd libcdio-paranoia-10.2+&libcdio-version;+1

./configure --prefix=/usr --disable-static &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Pour tester le résultat, tapez : <command>make check</command>.</para>
  
    <para>Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>
    user:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="content">
    <title>Contenu</title>

    <segmentedlist>
      <segtitle>Programmes installés</segtitle>
      <segtitle>Bibliothèque installée</segtitle>
      <segtitle>Répertoires installés</segtitle>

      <seglistitem>
        <seg>
          cd-drive,
          cd-info,
          cd-paranoia,
          cd-read,
          cdda-player,
          iso-info,
          iso-read, et
          mmc-tool
